title: ISic003655. I.Sicily inscription 003655
body:
Facsimile Images

1cross_greek
2ΑΣΥΛΛΙΣ

Apparatus criticus

Text of Manganaro 1965

translation

commentary

Two large letters are observable at right angles to the main text, on the left, which Manganaro reads as either two alphas or delta + alpha, but without any suggestion as to significance.
